rdt.tree.splitter

Class FullNominalActivateSplitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • rdt.tree.splitter.FullNominalSplitter
      • rdt.tree.splitter.FullNominalActivateSplitter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActiveSplitter, Splitter

    public class FullNominalActivateSplitter
extends FullNominalSplitter
implements ActiveSplitter
    Class for a full nominal splitter which can be activated. This splitter has the same functionality as the full nominal splitter except it can be activated or deactivated. If the splitter is deactivated it cannot process/handle any instance and if the splitter is activated it works as a full nominal splitter.

    MK
